Today Somgaga may be able to go window shopping for a R6 million house but that's because he started building the foundation of his castle when he was a little boy. And now he's just enjoying his throne. "We all have that one moment that was sign that we were born for greatness. For this pic. This Pvt jet thing I did it in apartheid days lol. This is from a movie I did with legendary The late cockytwobull. Be patient with yourself," he said. Not even Apartheid could stand in his way!A post shared by Somizi (@somizi) on Jun 6, 2017 at 10:47pm PDT